Toodles Galore
Toodles Galore is an attractive white female cat, who usually wears a large blue bow around her neck, and is supposedly Tom's girlfriend, although Tom is a reputed playboy, and had other love interests before and after Toodles. Toodles is the only love interest who appeared more than twice.